      </table>

      <h2 id="best-overall">Best Overall: 3-in-1 Wireless Charging Stand</h2>
      <p>The 3-in-1 wireless charging stand won because it is the only station in this comparison that charges all three devices reliably, without the alignment fiddling that makes cheaper stations frustrating. The magnetic phone alignment snaps an iPhone into the perfect charging position the moment you set it down, and the watch and earbuds slots hold their respective devices securely per manufacturer specifications.</p>
      <p>The vertical stand design is what makes this worth buying over a flat charging pad. A flat pad hides under papers and forces you to pick up the phone to check notifications. A vertical stand keeps the phone screen visible at a glance, so you can see incoming calls and messages without interrupting your work. The LED indicator is a thoughtful touch: a soft blue light confirms charging and auto-dims at night so it does not light up a dark bedroom.</p>
      <p>Heat management is the hidden differentiator. Wireless charging generates heat, and cheap stations let the phone get hot enough to throttle charging speed. This stand's aluminum base acts as a heatsink, and per manufacturer specifications, the phone stays cool enough to maintain full 15W charging speed throughout a two-hour session. The single wall plug is the final convenience — it replaces three adapters on your power strip, which matters when your desk already has a monitor, laptop, and lamp competing for outlets.</p>

      <div class="product-box">
        <h2>3-in-1 Wireless Charging Stand</h2>
